Present location: INSTITUT DE PAPYROLOGIE ET D'ÉGYPTOLOGIE, UNIVERSITÉ DE LILLE III [02/049] LILLE
Name: Model of a vase
Description: Model of a tubular vase without a neck, whose slightly bulging body is restricted in its upper section. It has a small, flat circular base with accumulations of clay and irregularities. See E27 031, 27 032, 27 033, 27 034, 27 036, 27 037.
